[vc_row pix_particles_check=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]Hi Readers!

Meet Digiperformer <strong>Bhavya Saxena</strong>, who is working as a Digital Marketing Trainer at <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210302201212/http://www.gndit.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Guru Nanak Dev Institute of Technology;</a> just after completing her dCDMC training at Digiperform.

In a chit-chat session, she has shared how Digiperform’s advanced digital marketing training program helped her to understand the concept of online marketing and trained her to follow her <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210302201212/https://digiperform.com/how-to-prepare-yourself-as-a-digital-marketing-trainer-2018/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">training career</a>.

Have a look!

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- It’s a pleasure to connect with you! Before heading further, we would like to know a bit about you.</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– Hi, I am Bhavya Saxena, currently working as a Digital Marketing Trainer at Guru Nanak Dev Institute of Technology.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- What originally attracted you to choose digital marketing as your career?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– Digital Marketing is one of the booming industries in India. It’s a very creative field, and it’s going to be our future now! Every business sooner or later will be dependent on it.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- What exactly makes us stand out from the competition &amp; urge you to choose us over others?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– Being a Digiperformer, I have seen the syllabus and the course and it’s very informative which covers every detail and topic right from the basics. We have been provided 24X7 access to LMS that contains all the study material and test papers which makes it better than other institutes.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- Tell us about your favorite experience you had with us, whether as a learner or as a customer?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– All the classroom sessions were fun, post-college, learning was never that easy. The trainers were very helpful and taught us in a very easy-to-learn way.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- Would you consider Digiperform as a trusted &amp; reliable resource for Digital marketing training? Why?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– Yes, with the helpful and cooperative staff around, it’s safe to say that Digiperform is a trusted and reliable resource.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- If you were to review our training program, what score would you give it out of 10?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– 8.5/10

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- Where do you see yourself in the next 5 years?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– I see myself as a known Digital Marketing Trainer and Influencer in some good institutions of India.

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform- If you had a piece of advice to someone just starting out, what would it be?</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– Stay Focused!

&nbsp;
<h4>Digiperform-Finally, Describe Digiperform in one line.</h4>
<strong>Bhavya</strong>– The perfect place to imbibe complete knowledge in Digital Marketing.

&nbsp;

Thanks, Bhavya for being a part of the Digiperform family.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]
